paragraphs.text:
%md
# 미세먼지 분석 개요
## 데이터 전처리
- UV : WitLab - CAS 140 CT
    - 항목 : UVB, EUVB, UVA, EUVA -> EUVB 위주로
    - 날짜 : 맑은날 (수기분류)
    - 시간 : 일출 ~ 일몰
    - UV 복사 세기 분단위 (W/m2) -> 누적량 (J/m2) -> aggregation (시간 누적, sum)
- 미세먼지 : 에어코리아 - 확정데이터
    - 측정 지점 : 전국 -> 천안 4지점
        - 성성동 : 도로변대기
        - 성황동 : 도시대기, 4.3km
        - 백석동 : 도시대기, 4.9km
        - 성거읍 : 도시대기, 6.2km, 2018년부터 시작
    - 측정 기간 : 2017년 ~ 2018년 3분기 (9월)
    - 전국 대기질 데이터 -> 천안 4지점 -> 미세먼지 등급 분류 -> agg. (일평균 미세먼지 등급, avg) -> agg. (일누적 미세먼지, sum)

paragraphs.title: final
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

udf_datetime2date = udf(lambda d: str(d)[0:4] + '-' + str(d)[4:6] + '-' + str(d)[6:8], StringType())
udf_datetime2hour = udf(lambda d: str(d)[8:], StringType())
udf_dnh2dh = udf(lambda d, h: d + ' ' + h, StringType())

df_cleandays = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///dayday/clean_days.parquet')

pm_cheonan = pm_final.where('location like "%천안%"')
pm_cheonan = pm_cheonan.select('station_name', 'datetime', 'pm10', 'pm25')\
                       .withColumn('date', udf_datetime2date('datetime'))\
                       .withColumn('hour', udf_datetime2hour('datetime'))\
                       .withColumn('pm10grade', udf_pm10grade('pm10'))\
                       .withColumn('pm25grade', udf_pm10grade('pm25'))\
                       .drop('datetime')\
                       .withColumn('datehour', udf_dnh2dh('date', 'hour'))\
                       .sort('datehour', 'station_name')
pm_cheonan.show()
pm_cheonan.createOrReplaceTempView('pm_cheonan')

paragraphs.title: uv
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

from pyspark.sql.types import DoubleType

udf_joule = udf(lambda val: val*60, DoubleType())

uv_srs = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///nl/witlab/cas/uv_srs.parquet')
df_uv = uv_srs.withColumn('datehour', udf_dt2dh('date', 'time'))\
              .withColumn('uvb_j', udf_joule('uvb'))\
              .withColumn('euvb_j', udf_joule('euvb'))\
              .drop('date', 'time', 'uvb', 'euvb', 'uva', 'duv', 'euv', 'euva')
df_uv.show()

df_uv = df_uv.groupby('datehour')\
             .agg({'uvb_j':'sum', 'euvb_j':'sum', 'uvi':'avg'})\
             .sort('datehour')\
             .withColumnRenamed('sum(euvb_j)', 'sum_euvb')\
             .withColumnRenamed('sum(uvb_j)', 'sum_uvb')\
             .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi)', 'avg_uvi')

df_uv.show()

paragraphs.title: uvpm
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark

df_uvpm = df_uv.join(pm_cheonan, 'datehour')
df_uvpm.show()
df_uvpm.createOrReplaceTempView('uvpm')

# save this df
df_uvpm.write.mode('overwrite').parquet('hdfs:///tmp/uvpm.parquet')

paragraphs.title: uvpm - daily agg.
paragraphs.text:
%pyspark
from pyspark.sql.types import IntegerType

udf_int = udf(lambda s: int(s), IntegerType())

uvpm_day = df_uvpm.drop('hour', 'datehour', 'mdh', 'sum(uvb_j)')\
                  .groupby('date', 'year', 'month', 'day', 'station_name')\
                  .agg({'sum_euvb': 'sum',
                        'avg_uvi': 'avg',
                        'pm10': 'sum',
                        'pm25': 'sum',
                        'pm10grade': 'avg',
                        'pm25grade': 'avg',
                  })

uvpm_day = uvpm_day.withColumn('avg(pm10grade)', udf_int('avg(pm10grade)'))\
                   .withColumn('avg(pm25grade)', udf_int('avg(pm25grade)'))\
                   .withColumnRenamed('avg(pm10grade)', 'avg_pm10grade')\
                   .withColumnRenamed('avg(pm25grade)', 'avg_pm25grade')
uvpm_day.show()
uvpm_day.createOrReplaceTempView('uvpm_day')

%sql

select * from uvpm_day
where (avg_pm10grade = 1 or avg_pm10grade = 3)
and station_name = '성성동'
order by avg_pm10grade, date
